  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA9">
<l>numakkaṭiyō maṉṟeṉṟu nonturaitteṉ mālār</l>
<l>tamakkavarttāñ cārvariya rāṉā lemakkiṉi</l>
<l>yātāṉu mākiṭukā ṇeñcē yavarttiṟattē</l>
<l>yātāṉuñ cintit tiru.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What [is] painfully repeating “we are your servants” to him</l>
<l>who is great? Because he himself is difficult to approach, be by anything</l>
<l>for us now, see, heart, sit thinking by anything</l>
<l>on his account.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
